**why —** It is the part that outlived the obscurity: a score people quote who never finished the climb — the music that made a dying tree sing.

**how —** Crystallized from Faxanadu (NES 1989) — Famicom Xanadu, on Falcom's licensed Xanadu name.

**◌ the mythos —** It is the part that outlived the obscurity: a score people quote who never finished the climb — the music that made a dying tree sing. a being of the World Tree and the climb to the Evil One

